                {
                    "system": "phone",
                    "use": "work",
                    "value": "01234567890"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
```

 #### Requirements

 Identifies who created this task.  May be used by access control mechanisms (e.g., to ensure that only the creator can cancel a task).

